Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.00,0:23:18.70,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}散落滿地的記憶之砂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.87,0:23:22.67,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}芽生えた想いまで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.87,0:23:22.67,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}以及萌生的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.78,0:23:27.63,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}ねえ　こんなに呆気なく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.78,0:23:27.63,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}你看  卻是那麼輕易
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.62,0:23:34.92,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}消えてしまうの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.62,0:23:34.92,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}消失殆盡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.96,0:23:36.01,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}I wish I was there
