Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.69,0:23:53.82,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}不  請不要對生命無愛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.90,0:23:55.74,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}This endless dead end
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.90,0:23:55.74,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}儘管這絕望  不竭不衰
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.90,0:24:00.37,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}君を砕くこの悲しみが
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.90,0:24:00.37,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}願那讓你苦不堪言的悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.49,0:24:05.71,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}いつか終わりますように
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.49,0:24:05.71,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}會迎來完結的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.91,0:24:09.50,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}For now I'll see you off
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.91,0:24:09.50,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}而我卻要目送你離開
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.42,0:24:12.80,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}And we'll die
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.42,0:24:12.80,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}我們終將會重來
